{"id":"143279762a73e3e05963b3184b40378b4a8e1c24059e16e484db01a143fdd654","item_id":"18fabf4082:0","text":"若要让 RenderMan 控制几何设置，可以在"}
{"id":"c891df73080a1f0bead1c02a57f84f1e1242d4ac902c189c4f793618f0d5ac54","item_id":"18fabf4082:1","text":"RenderGeometrySettings"}
{"id":"3412b88ffdf62545b16c1292b28f7aa3d1902a1795c2b16b1974715186bd68d3","item_id":"18fabf4082:2","text":"LOP 的 RenderMan 选项卡中找到这些设置"}
{"id":"2e5f32e0d08ddc780910d9a31b36af4766dce19dbab003bfc92ce6cdc1b055e6","item_id":"18fabf4082:3","text":"（需要安装 RfH）"}
{"id":"c7f937836f5d82d53bc507752075f87e25009ec11bc9fd4e282f0b645e47af7c","item_id":"18fabf4082:4","text":"选择"}
{"id":"16aec665b4a8055a805a802c8c7d824825cdbdedbd88ed248326a5621a7c416c","item_id":"18fabf4082:5","text":"Set or Create（设置或创建）"}
{"id":"7175517a370b5cd2e664e3fd29c4ea9db5ce17058eb9772fe090a5485e49dad6","item_id":"18fabf4082:6","text":"或"}
{"id":"05173d20d6ab25990802fb9686fd3c9c459fcca75c9d76ba15c4279ac8f48c0e","item_id":"18fabf4082:7","text":"Set if Exists（若存在则设置）"}
{"id":"fe1c0448bade71be54e758833d16e0981d17a2cac947d52b35469f06ba7e96c1","item_id":"18fabf4082:8","text":"来创建或更改 geometry attribute（几何属性）上的 opinion（意见），或选择"}
{"id":"211d0bb8cf4f5b5202c2a9b7996e483898644aa24714b1e10edd80a54ba4b560","item_id":"18fabf4082:9","text":"Block（阻断）"}
{"id":"5cb1d5b3fcf480740686410cadd2ca9fc61afcd0450143cfb1e4936fac5967f2","item_id":"18fabf4082:10","text":"来禁用该 attribute 上已有的 opinions（意见）。所有可用参数都会列出，但默认均未设置。"}
{"id":"99bd94ada380007ca9388852bc101fbcd3102b3591763ab22f3faf5af559d457","item_id":"18fabf4082:11","text":"这些设置与 object nodes（对象节点）上的 RenderMan spare parameter 选项卡中可以找到的设置相同。"}
